  <div class="row">
    <div class="col s12 m12">
      <div class="card large hoverable">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://www.culinarydepotinc.com/Content/Images/uploaded/blog%20uploads/bbq%20catering%20finale.jpg">
          <span class="card-title pic-words">Special Menus</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <p>Business lunches and dinners, family-gatherings, weddings and rehearsal dinners, receptions, company barbecues, holiday parties, you name it. 
